## Market Data (for the pitch deck built into the app)

| Metric | Value |
|---|---|
| Demat accounts | 22.5 crore (March 2026) |
| Active investors | ~⅓ of total accounts |
| Unique MF investors | 5.9 crore |
| Monthly SIP inflows | ₹32,087 crore (March 2026) |
| MF AUM | ₹81.01 lakh crore |
| UPI users | 350-500 million |
| Smartphone users | ~1 billion |
| MF penetration | ~4.2% of population |
| Rural saving intent | 96% want to invest |

### TAM Calculation
- **Total:** 500M UPI users who can transact digitally
- **SAM:** 100M users in Tier 2/3 cities with income but no investment guidance  
- **SOM (Year 1):** 5M users through viral referral + WhatsApp sharing

